snippet.title: Stars Share Their Ins & Outs For 2026
snippet.description:
From bath salts to flip flops, movie and TV actors reveal their 2026 ins and outs. Featuring submissions from Becky Lynch, Catalina Moreno, Jack O'Connell, Jessica Williams, Madelaine Petsch, Sam Rockwell, Sasha Calle, the cast of Tell Me Lies, and more!
